[indistinct chattering]

01:36.583 --> 01:38.583
♪ Tell you how it's going down
Kelly E-V-E we comin' through ♪

01:38.583 --> 01:40.625
♪ And got 'em bowin' down ladies
can you feel it it's an anthem ♪

01:40.625 --> 01:42.583
♪ You can bounce around give you
