17:07.625 --> 17:09.834
Well, that must've been
one hell of a talk.

17:09.834 --> 17:11.375
- Sort of.
- Ha ha.

17:11.375 --> 17:13.458
- Yeah.
- Yeah.

17:13.458 --> 17:15.625
Well, I just...
I wanted to thank you.

17:15.625 --> 17:18.165
I mean, what you did,
it means the world to me, so...

17:18.165 --> 17:20.541
- The pie's on me, heh.
- Thank you.

17:20.541 --> 17:22.750
I wish I could do more for you,
but I'm sort of broke

17:22.750 --> 17:25.541
at the moment, you know, um...

17:25.541 --> 17:27.666
...but if you, if you ever need
anything, anything at all

17:27.666 --> 17:30.375
I mean, just come
and talk to me, alright?

17:30.375 --> 17:32.500
- Alright.
- Alright.

17:34.000 --> 17:35.542
You...

17:35.542 --> 17:38.125
...you wanna sit for a second?

17:38.125 --> 17:39.458
Yeah, sure.

17:41.875 --> 17:43.417
Something on your mind?

17:45.208 --> 17:48.166
I've been getting a lot
of pressure to go visit Jake.

17:48.166 --> 17:50.375
- How come?
- We used to date.

17:50.375 --> 17:53.834
- And he's been asking for me.
- Oh.

17:53.834 --> 17:56.500
He committed a crime and let you

17:56.500 --> 17:57.834
an innocent guy
go to jail for it.

17:57.834 --> 17:59.083
The way I see it

17:59.083 --> 18:00.875
he doesn't deserve any visitors.

18:00.875 --> 18:02.708
You want me to be
honest with you?

18:02.708 --> 18:04.542
Of course, I do.

18:04.542 --> 18:06.041
I mean, I-I, uh...

18:06.041 --> 18:07.500
I guess I've never
really thought about it

18:07.500 --> 18:12.166
but...I kind of want
to see the kid suffer.

18:13.959 --> 18:16.542
But to say he doesn't deserve
visitors, I don't know.

18:16.542 --> 18:19.583
I mean, that's a bad place.

18:19.583 --> 18:22.500
The guy needs support,
no matter what he's done.

18:24.208 --> 18:25.750
I'm sure as hell
not gonna go visit him

18:25.750 --> 18:27.750
but...you know, I like the idea

18:27.750 --> 18:30.333
that somebody somewhere is.

18:30.333 --> 18:31.959
Wow.

18:31.959 --> 18:34.458
That's not what you wanted
to hear me say, is it? I...

18:34.458 --> 18:36.959
You know what? I just...

18:36.959 --> 18:38.458
I owe you so much.

18:39.792 --> 18:41.333
And I just,
I don't feel comfortable

18:41.333 --> 18:43.291
lying to you about it.

18:43.291 --> 18:44.708
I value honesty.

18:44.708 --> 18:46.708
Well, I'm glad to hear that.

18:48.166 --> 18:49.458
Who knows? Maybe someday
I'll change my mind.

18:49.458 --> 18:50.959
I'll go pay him a visit myself.

18:50.959 --> 18:53.291
I think you would scare
the crap out of him.

18:53.291 --> 18:54.417
I know.

18:54.417 --> 18:55.750
[both laughing]

18:55.750 --> 18:58.166
- Enjoy your pie.
- Thanks.

