how much I missed you.

38:33.959 --> 38:36.792
Then why didn't you call me?

38:36.792 --> 38:40.500
And why did you hook up
with Vicky?

38:40.500 --> 38:43.125
Because I knew I'd have to be
honest with you

38:43.125 --> 38:45.625
about what happened with Marti.

38:45.625 --> 38:48.417
And I didn't think
you could forgive me for that

38:48.417 --> 38:52.041
or that I, that I had
the right to ask you to.

38:53.667 --> 38:55.542
Ask me.

38:59.959 --> 39:02.166
